            <p>
                <span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family: TimesNewRomanPSMT;">4.1 </span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">确定伤残</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">类别</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">:评定伤残时,应</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">根</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">据人体的身体结</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">构</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">与</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">功</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">能</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">损</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">伤情况确定所涉及的
伤残</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">类别</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">。</span></span>
            </p>
            <p>
                <span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family: TimesNewRomanPSMT;">4.2 </span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">确定伤残等</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">级</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">:应</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">根</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">据伤残情况,在同</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">类别</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">伤残下,确定伤残等</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">级</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">。<br/></span><span style="font-family: TimesNewRomanPSMT;">4.3 </span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">确定保险金给付比例:应</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">根</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">据伤残等</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">级</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">对应的</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">百分</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">比,确定保险金给付比例。<br/></span><span style="font-family: TimesNewRomanPSMT;">4.4 </span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">多处</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">伤残的评定</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">原</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">则:当同一保险事故造成</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">两处</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">或</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">两处</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">以上伤残时,应</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">首</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">先对各</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">处</span></span>
            </p>
            <p>
                <span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family: SimSun;">伤残</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">程度分别</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">进行评定,如</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">果几处</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">伤残等</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">级</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">不同,以</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">最重</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">的伤残等</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">级</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">作为</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">最</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">终的评定结</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">论</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">如</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">果两处</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">或</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">两处</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">以上伤残等</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">级</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">相同,伤残等</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">级</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">在</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">原</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">评定</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">基础</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">上</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">最多晋升</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">一</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">级</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">,</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">最高晋升至</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">第一</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">级</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">。同一部</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">位</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">和</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">性质</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">的伤残,不应采用本标准条</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">文两</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">条以上或者同一条</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">文两次</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">以上进行
评定。</span></span>
            </p>
