            <p>  本标准中的发声和言语的功能障碍是指语言功能丧失。</p>
            <p>
                <span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family: FangSong;">注:语言功能完全丧失指</span><span style="font-family: FangSong;">构</span><span style="font-family: FangSong;">成语言的口</span><span style="font-family: FangSong;">唇音</span><span style="font-family: FangSong;">、</span><span style="font-family: FangSong;">齿舌音</span><span style="font-family: FangSong;">、口</span><span style="font-family: FangSong;">盖音</span><span style="font-family: FangSong;">和</span><span style="font-family: FangSong;">喉头音</span><span style="font-family: FangSong;">的</span><span style="font-family: FangSong;">四种</span><span style="font-family: FangSong;">语言功能中,
