                        <span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family: SimSun;">4</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">.3 </span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">肺</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">的结</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">构损</span><span style="font-family: SimSun;">伤</span></span>
